---
---

<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center bg-gradient-to-br from-wave-blue-dark via-wave-blue to-wave-blue-light overflow-hidden">

  <!-- Background decorative waves -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 560" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-full h-full">
      <path d="M0 280 C180 200, 360 160, 540 280 C720 400, 900 440, 1080 280 C1260 120, 1380 200, 1440 280 L1440 560 L0 560 Z" fill="white"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 opacity-15" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <path d="M0 100 C240 40, 480 160, 720 100 C960 40, 1200 160, 1440 100 L1440 200 L0 200 Z" fill="#E8638B"/>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 text-center">

    <!-- Badge -->
    <span class="inline-block bg-wave-peach/20 text-wave-peach border border-wave-peach/30 text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6 backdrop-blur-sm">
      Swim Analysis &amp; Coaching &bull; Redcliffe, Brisbane
    </span>

    <!-- Headline -->
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
      Hey, I'm Chelsea.<br />
      <span class="text-wave-peach">Let's work on your swim.</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- Subheading -->
    <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-blue-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
      Triathletes have the engine but they often lack the feel for the water.
      With a background in National-level competitive swimming, I'll help you bridge the
      gap between your effort and your results.
    </p>

    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a
        href="#about"
        class="bg-white text-wave-blue hover:bg-wave-blue-light font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
      >
        A Bit About Me
      </a>
      <a
        href="#booking"
        class="bg-wave-pink hover:bg-wave-pink-dark text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg transition-all duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
      >
        Let's Chat
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- Wave divider at bottom -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 80" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none" class="w-full">
      <path d="M0 40 C360 80, 1080 0, 1440 40 L1440 80 L0 80 Z" fill="white"/>
    </svg>
  </div>

</section>
